    	<div class="teaser-image"><a href="/article/five-facts-about-the-big-bang?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark">

<div class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-teaser">
  
        <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/2015_teaser/public/images/standard/bb1.gif?itok=3xL2GYh_" width="736" height="414" alt="Galaxy with question marks hanging from sky with kids grabbing at them " typeof="foaf:Image" />



  </div>




</a></div>
    
  <div class="teaser-date">08/23/16</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/five-facts-about-the-big-bang?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span property="schema:name">Five facts about the Big Bang</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>It&rsquo;s the cornerstone of cosmology, but what is it all about?</p>


</article>
